---
title: "US59 — Monitor content + listings"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as System Administrator
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>MonitorScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>ModerateContent
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>Post · ExpertService · Deliverable
  A->>B: open reported content queue
  B->>C: loadReports()
  C->>E: listReportedContent()
  E-->>C: List of reported Post / ExpertService / Deliverable
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (reports)
  A->>B: tap Remove on an item
  B->>C: remove(contentId)
  C->>E: removeContent(contentId)
  E-->>C: ok (content removed)
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (updated)
  B-->>A: content no longer visible to users
  note over E: listReportedContent / removeContent via SupabaseGateway (RLS admin-only)
